# Spider-Electron

Desktop web crawler (Electron). Read `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` before editing crawler, IPC, or UI logic.

## Key files

- `src/main/main.js` — crawler (BFS, fetch, cheerio, robots.txt)
- `src/preload/preload.js` — IPC whitelist, `window.api`
- `src/renderer/renderer.js` — UI, CSV export
- `src/renderer/index.html` — layout

## After code changes

If behavior, IPC, constants, data models, deps, or file structure changed — update `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` in the same session (see `docs/DOC_MAINTENANCE.md` checklist). Update the "Останнє оновлення" date in ARCHITECTURE.md.

## Conventions

- Network requests only in main process.
- New IPC channels: update preload whitelist + main + renderer.
- Match existing style: minimal scope, no over-abstraction.
- UI text is Ukrainian; match unless user requests otherwise.
